{"title":"Guinea pig questions","link":"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/882124958/0/marginalrevolution~Guinea-pig-questions.html","date":1713725209000,"content":"<p>If someone demographically normal and not especially at-risk wants to serve as a guinea pig, what is the optimal allocation of that resource?</p>\r\n<p>Is there any formal discussion of this question? I know they say “there is always an Effective Altruism blog post,” but is there?</p>\r\n<p>Mostly I have medicine and medical experimentation in mind, but I can imagine other answers as well, such as “trying to leap forty flaming cars with a motorcycle.”  Though I doubt that one will end up as the winner.  In any case, I am assuming away legal constraints.  Where can you volunteer as a guinea pig for the highest social value?</p>\r\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2024/04/guinea-pig-questions.html\">Guinea pig questions</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://marginalrevolution.com\">Marginal REVOLUTION</a>.</p>\r\n<img height=\"1\" width=\"1\" src=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/i/882124958/0/marginalrevolution\" />\r\n<div><a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/28/882124958/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/fblike20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/29/882124958/marginalrevolution,\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/pinterest20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/24/882124958/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/x.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/19/882124958/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/email20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/20/882124958/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/rss20.png\" /><